                <head>252. Editorial Note</head>
                <p>On December 17, the Operations Coordinating Board reviewed and revised an
                    Operations Plan for Greece dated December 12. The Operations Plan adopted on
                    December 17 contained minor revisions to the text of the May 21 Operations Plan
                        (<ref target="#d241">Document 241</ref>). The text of the December 17
                    Operations Plan is in Department of State, <gloss target="#t_OCB1">OCB</gloss>
                    Files: Lot 62 <gloss target="#t_D1">D</gloss> 430, Greece. Minutes of the
                    December 17 <gloss target="#t_OCB1">OCB</gloss> meeting are <hi rend="italic"
                        >Ibid</hi>., Minutes VII.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
